XLII_CheckAdmiralRep 0.50","AddText ""An uniformed officer - Alliance security, shoulder patch of the XLII - falls into step alongside you as you move through the docking concourse. He doesn't slow. He doesn't look at you. Something is pressed into your hand. He keeps walking.""",,"1:blind_eye_look:Look at the note.","Act 1 note delivery. MarketPostDock fires after docking. Wins over marketDock (score 0) when conditions are met."
XLII_blind_eye_note_look,DialogOptionSelected,"$option == blind_eye_look","AddText ""A folded slip. No name. No signature.""
AddText ""Three lines, printed.""
AddText ""Ring-Port. Transponder off. Ask for Korrin.""
AddText ""By the time you look up, the officer has cleared the checkpoint and is gone.""",,"1:blind_eye_pocket:Continue",
XLII_blind_eye_note_pocket,DialogOptionSelected,"$option == blind_eye_pocket","$global.XLII_blindEyeNoteReceived = true
