$tag:XLII_elias_korrin
$global.XLII_blindEyeDeclined
!$global.XLII_blindEyeMissionActive","ShowPersonVisual
FireAll XLII_EliasReturnOptions","He answers without delay. The expression is the same as when you left it - almost. ""Commander.""",,"Return visit after declining. Offers accept or leave."
