# Act 3 - Post-Victory,,,,,,
XLII_elias_victory,OpenCDE,"$isPerson
$tag:XLII_elias_korrin
$global.XLII_ringPortTaken
!$global.XLII_blindEyeVictoryAcked","ShowPersonVisual
FireAll XLII_EliasVictoryIntro","You comm Korrin from the dock. The line connects without routing delay - Ring-Port's comms infrastructure already back under Alliance administration. The station is different. Same bulkheads, same corridors. Different faces at every checkpoint.",,"First visit to Elias after Ring-Port is taken. One-time acknowledgment."
XLII_elias_victory_intro,XLII_EliasVictoryIntro,,,"""It's done. Good job."" 

He says it without embellishment.

""August's contingent moved in within the hour. They'll be staged two berths over, waiting on their signal, but for all intents and purposes, the station is already under Alliance administration.""","1:elias_victory_what:What happens next?
2:elias_victory_ack:Understood.",
XLII_elias_victory_what,DialogOptionSelected,"$option == elias_victory_what",,"""August's people hold the station before the Office arrives. That was the point."" He closes the terminal display. ""The Fleet Admiral will know what was accomplished here. Whatever the Office makes of that is their concern.""","1:elias_victory_close:Understood.",
XLII_elias_victory_close,DialogOptionSelected,"$option == elias_victory_close","$global.XLII_blindEyeVictoryAcked = true
EndConversation",,,"Sets XLII_blindEyeVictoryAcked and closes dialog."
