XLII_admiral_ext_midquest_opt,XLII_AdmiralMainMenu,"$tag:XLII_fleet_admiral_emil
XLII_IsRingPortTakenExternally
$global.XLII_blindEyeNoteReceived
!$global.XLII_blindEyeComplete",,,"1:ring_port_ext_midquest:About Ring-Port.","Mid-quest external capture. Player had the note but assault never happened."
XLII_admiral_ext_prequest_init,DialogOptionSelected,"$option == ring_port_ext_prequest
$tag:XLII_fleet_admiral_emil","FireAll XLII_AugustExtPrequestContent","""Ring-Port is no longer in hostile hands."" A pause. The distorted figure is still for a moment longer than usual. ""We are aware. The circumstances are not what I had planned, but the outcome serves the Alliance regardless.""",,"Pre-quest opening. August acknowledges without revealing his operation."
XLII_august_ext_prequest_body,XLII_AugustExtPrequestContent,,,"""The Office will need to establish presence before the situation calcifies. My people were not in position."" He does not elaborate further. ""That is a complication I will manage.""","1:ring_port_ext_helped:I had a hand in that.
2:ring_port_ext_info:Thought you should know.","Player chooses to claim credit or stay neutral."
XLII_august_ext_prequest_helped,DialogOptionSelected,"$option == ring_port_ext_helped
$tag:XLII_fleet_admiral_emil","FireAll XLII_AugustExtPrequestReward","""Then I suppose Alliance owes you a debt that predates the paperwork."" A beat. ""I had an operation planned for that station. Months of preparation. You have made it unnecessary.""

You detect the hint of frustration, however faint as he keys something on his console.

""Some credits and a marker of trust. For your 'initiate'...""",,"Player claims credit. August is pragmatic - the outcome serves regardless."
XLII_august_ext_prequest_info,DialogOptionSelected,"$option == ring_port_ext_info
$tag:XLII_fleet_admiral_emil","FireAll XLII_AugustExtPrequestReward","""Noted."" The distorted figure makes a gesture that might be acknowledgment. ""The Alliance benefits regardless of who held the blade.""

He keys something on the console.

""A small transfer. For services rendered to the Alliance - whether you intended them or not.""",,"Neutral path. August still pays - the intel alone has value."
XLII_august_ext_prequest_reward,XLII_AugustExtPrequestReward,,"XLII_DeliverExternalReward 500000
$global.XLII_ringPortTaken = true
$global.XLII_ringPortTakenExternally = true
$global.XLII_blindEyeVictoryAcked = true
$global.XLII_blindEyeComplete = true
FireAll XLII_AdmiralMainMenu",,,"Delivers 500K credits. Sets all resolution flags."
XLII_admiral_ext_midquest_init,DialogOptionSelected,"$option == ring_port_ext_midquest
$tag:XLII_fleet_admiral_emil","FireAll XLII_AugustExtMidquestContent","The line is quiet for a few brief seconds. When he speaks, the modulated voice carries something that might be controlled anger, might be exhaustion.

""Ring-Port has changed hands."" A pause. ""Not through the channels I arranged. Not through my terms. Not through any of the infrastructure my people spent months embedding in that station.""",,"Mid-quest opening. August is displeased - controlled, not explosive."
XLII_august_ext_midquest_body,XLII_AugustExtMidquestContent,,,"He leans back. The encryption ripples.

""The Office arrived to a situation already in motion. My contingent was not in position. The embedded personnel - Loss. The operational security we built - compromised."" He does not raise his voice.

""I do not question the outcome. Ring-Port is out of hostile hands. But the operation I designed was not about the station, Commander. It was about who controlled the transition. That window is closed.""

He keys something on the console. The gesture is clipped.

""Credits. The contract rate for the outcome, absent the method. Take it. Consider the matter closed.""","1:ring_port_ext_mid_ack:Understood.","August pays the reduced rate. The operation's value was in control, not conquest."
XLII_august_ext_midquest_close,DialogOptionSelected,"$option == ring_port_ext_mid_ack
$tag:XLII_fleet_admiral_emil","XLII_DeliverExternalReward 500000
