# Octantis Quest,,,,,,
XLII_nanoforge_discuss_eligible,DialogOptionSelected,"$option == XLII_nanoforge_discuss
$tag:XLII_fleet_admiral_emil
XLII_CheckAdmiralRep
!$global.XLII_nanoforgeQuestOffered","$global.XLII_nanoforgeQuestOffered = true","""There is one thing."" A brief pause that, for once, doesn't feel like a tactic. ""Something the Alliance needs - not just for the war effort. But for what comes after it.

Kori's yards can produce hulls well enough. But what we cannot produce - not yet - is the precision manufacturing infrastructure we lost during the civil war. A Pristine Nanoforge. Domain-era. Undamaged.

If you come across one, bring it to me directly."" The encrypted silhouette leans forward slightly. ""I won't ask where you found it. You won't need to ask what we intend to do with it.""

A brief pause.

""The Alliance does not forget its debts, Commander.""","1:return_to_main_menu:Understood.",
XLII_nanoforge_discuss_fallback,DialogOptionSelected,"$option == XLII_nanoforge_discuss
$tag:XLII_fleet_admiral_emil",,"""You've served us well enough, Commander - that's not in question."" A measured pause. ""But some matters I hold in reserve for those who've given the Alliance more... comprehensive proof of commitment.

Keep doing what you're doing. That conversation will happen when the time is right.""","1:return_to_main_menu:Understood.",
XLII_nanoforge_deliver_success,DialogOptionSelected,"$option == XLII_nanoforge_deliver
$tag:XLII_fleet_admiral_emil
$global.XLII_nanoforgeQuestOffered
XLII_NanoforgeExchange check
!$global.XLII_nanoforgeQuestComplete","XLII_NanoforgeExchange give
$global.XLII_nanoforgeQuestComplete = true
AddCredits 500000
AddStoryPoints 5","The silhouette on the screen is still for a long moment.

""Some things are better kept off the record. But thank you, truly.""

You hear something being keyed in the background.

""The forge goes to Kori. What it produces will outlast both of us."" A pause - the first one that doesn't feel calculated. ""I have something for you, in return. A part of what the Alliance Intelligence Office has held since end of the war.""

Data streams to your command console - encrypted manifests, operational assessments, a transfer authorization bearing August's personal cipher.

""Octantis, or at least a uplink to it. I've been advised not to speculate - but it will serve your fleet well. I have it on authority that it performs."" A brief silence before the connection modulates.

""Needless to say, do not lose it, Commander. We try to avoid giving these out freely.""","1:dismiss:End transmission",
"#END Octantis Quest",,,,,,

